  | volume = 127
  | issue = 1
  | pages = 93–111
  | date = 1997-03
  | doi = 10.1006/icar.1996.5669
| bibcode=1997Icar..127...93S}}</ref>與木衛四在[[後期重轟炸期|後期重轟炸期]]受到更多、更劇烈的撞擊<ref name = "Baldwin">{{cite web
  | last = Baldwin
